comments: Johnson (BKN) makes contact with the part of Achiuwa's (TOR) hand that is still touching the ball during the latter's tip-in attempt at the rim.
Johnson (BKN) makes contact to Achiuwa's (TOR) hand and affects his shot near the rim.
There is no clear and conclusive angle showing Achiuwa (TOR) makes last contact with the ball prior to it going out of bounds.
Young (TOR) reaches in and is not in a legal guarding position when contact occurs to the front of Curry (BKN) during the drive that impacts his SQBR.

Aldridge (BKN) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of Trent Jr. (TOR) and some contact occurs to the side of the latter that is marginal and does not impact his defensive play.
Johnson (BKN) lifts his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Achiuwa (TOR) makes some marginal contact to the right arm of Johnson (BKN) but the contact does not impact the dunk attempt at the rim.
Mills (BKN) legally contests the driving shot attempt from Trent Jr. (TOR).
Trent Jr. (TOR) reaches in and grazes the fingertips of Johnson (BKN) as he gathers the ball. The marginal contact does not impact Johnson's handling of the ball.
Aldridge (BKN) makes marginal contact to Young's (BKN) back while rebounding.
Curry (BKN) makes contact to Trent's (TOR) body which affects his driving shot attempt.
Trent Jr. (TOR) slides in front of Curry (GSW) during the driving shot attempt and does not make any arm contact. The shot is then legally blocked by Barnes (TOR).

Barnes (TOR) places a forearm to the back of Aldridge (BKN) during the rebound but does not extend his arm further into Aldridge as the ball comes off of the rim. Aldridge's reaction is not consistent with the level of contact.
Brown (BKN) moves into the body of Trent Jr. (TOR) and impacts his SQBR during his dribble up the floor.
Brown (BKN) reaches in and makes contact with the left arm of Trent Jr. (TOR) and pulls it off of the ball.
Johnson (BKN) gathers the ball and comes to legal stop prior to beginning his dribble.
Young (TOR) legally contests the jump shot from Johnson (BKN).
Johnson (BKN) leans forward during his jump shot attempt and lands into the stationary Young (TOR), who was legally contesting the jump shot.
